allorsUnifiedGood.name: EINSA CC 1.5
allorsUnifiedGood.description:
- The Baggage Cart, model CC 1.5 has been specially designed to transport and collect all kinds of packages and baggage in airports, docks, railway stations and industrial plants.
- This cart covers a wide range of needs in the transporting of cargo and lightweight packages.
- The design of the cart is based on the standardization principle; all different applications have the same mechanical solutions.
- The cart is simple to handle and requires minimum maintenance.
